# Test patch

#primitive FM Oscillator

+ phasor carrier
+ phasor mod
+ mult fmdepth
+ add modadd
+ phasor pitcher
+ mult pitcherdepth
+ add pitchmod

= 0.01 pitcher@freq
> pitcher@out pitcherdepth@in1
= 440 pitcherdepth@in2
= 110 pitchmod@in1
> pitcherdepth@out pitchmod@in2
> pitchmod@out modadd@in1

= 200 mod@freq

> mod@out fmdepth@in1
= 900 fmdepth@in2

> fmdepth@out modadd@in2
> modadd@out carrier@freq
> carrier@out out@l
> carrier@out out@r

